# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

##0.3 - 2018-11-30
### Added
- Further database integration. 
- Sends the front end some more interesting data
- Mocked login functionality

## 0.2 - 2018-11-16
### Added
- An advanced profile route that queries the database
- An advanced enroll route that queries and updates the database
- Integration with the frontend
- More tests

## 0.1 - 2018-11-2
### Added
- A basic signout route
- A basic profile route
- A basic home route
- A profile route that queries our database

### Bugs
- Our database connection with AWS is currently broken, doesn't cause errors, but profile route doesn't function as expected.

## 0.0.2 - 2018-10-28
### Added
- A basic signin route that returns basic JSON atm
- Refactored the Buffalo project to be an API, not full Web-App

## 0.0.1 - 2018-10-24
### Added
- This CHANGELOG file to hopefully serve as an evolving example of a
  standardized open source project CHANGELOG.
- Implemented Golang, Buffalo-based boilerplate
